/**
 * Vehicle Data — Brand → Model → Year hierarchy
 *
 * v2 architecture: NO runtime WC API calls.
 * Vehicle hierarchy is loaded from a build-time generated JSON cache.
 * Cache is generated by scripts/generate-vehicle-cache.ts
 */

